OL,5,G0035 It'll Be Alright on the Night
OL,6,     FTom Allen presents another
OL,7,     Fcollection of outtakes from
OL,8,     Fdramas, comedies and entertainment
OL,9,     Fshows alongside on-air mishaps
OL,10,     Ffrom the world of news, daytime TV
OL,11,     Fand sport. Featuring clips of Ant
OL,12,     Fand Dec, Ralf Little, Jill Scott,
OL,13,     FRicky Tomlinson, Prue Leith,
OL,14,     FWarwick Davis and many more, with
OL,15,     Fthe cock-ups including Bradley
OL,16,     FWalsh falling over during a
OL,17,     Frecording of Blankety Blank.
